2. In these Rules-
               “Class I wharf” means a public wharf not used as such before
                   the 1st day of January, 1966;
               “Class II wharf” means any public wharf which is not a Class I
                   wharf;
               “wharf” includes-
                   (a) plant and equipment used for the purposes of a whad;
                   (b) such passenger handling facilities used in connection
                        therewith as may be approved by the Minister.
                                 PARTII. Alteration of Twig
